Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美麗了  真紀小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我真紀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的又大又勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  阿勝  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝  我快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真紀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝  我們一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,片名：明日的雪之丞２
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小明  妳很閒的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經寫完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換晶子的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳太會吃東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我會等你的  你快點抄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千春  小勝有來過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇佐見  你是說前部長久保勝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對哦  妳成為社團經理的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝已經住院  妳並沒有見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我是看過他  也聽過他的謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說他是訓練時出事  住院很長一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直找他  要他回社團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請他至少來看練習  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習中把他打傷的雪村  後來轉學了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說他們倆是公認的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們根本比不上他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去問阿勝何時回社團  他卻對我這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:06:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邊笑邊說  我不打拳擊了  我感到害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打擾他約會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟水島明約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涼月學園數一數二的秀才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優等生的水島刻意把成績考糟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟留級的久保一起  課後補習的原因你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她對朋友說是由於  離婚的母親開始交往新男友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實她的成績急速惡化  正好在久保住院的那段期間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心與焦燥  可能一直埋藏在水島心中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從久保平安出院後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好她是為了得到  兩人在一起的快樂時光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而刻意讓成績倒退的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不打拳擊  跑去約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天起要去療養所復健？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生建議我利用春假
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:08:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去做復健恢復  住院昏睡期退化的身體機能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並脫離精神壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快去趕快去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到不用再看到你這陰陽怪氣的臉  我就輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有點遺憾  不能吃到晶子的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳講得輕鬆  小明  我看妳最好學學作菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是為了將來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你雞婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼態度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我跟晶子道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳真是怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一章  紅色記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很吵耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不想回涼月學園嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥  巴士來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥  你不能太勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好不容易開始康復
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的外套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在依然找不到兇手…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久保勝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是涼月學園的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有自我介紹  我叫做櫻瀨由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在走廊跟體育館有幾次擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我是拳擊社的迷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在這裡療養？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有氣喘病  所以經常往返這裡與學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復健完以後  你會回拳擊社吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待  看到你站上擂台的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（拳擊社）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天凌晨發生的運鈔車  被搶事件的犯人依然找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警方擴大搜索範圍  依靠現場的遺留物…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美麗了  真紀小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喊我真紀就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真紀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:17:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真紀  要去了哦  真紀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的身體還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的景色  沒想到有這樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  來吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把毛巾洗一洗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的也好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳吃太多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你好像很沒食慾嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在想一下事情耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飽了  幫我謝謝晶子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對阿勝的感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  趁現在趕快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你  你要溫柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.81,0:23:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  好有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直暗戀著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.68,0:23:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗戀著擂台上的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再激烈一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像擂台上的你那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要  還要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.38,0:23:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.67,0:25:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（待續）
